            <h2 class="font-heading text-h1 lg:text-h1-desktop">Our Process</h2>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="prose text-body-xs lg:text-body-small">
              <p>
                As leaders in the field of infant formulas, we believe in the power of science and innovation, combined with
                the wisdom of nature, to create the most effective infant formulas for athletes and active individuals.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

